}]]>
                        </programlisting>
                        <para>
                            that was already compiling and running, still wrong though:
                        </para>
                        <screen>
<![CDATA[$ g++ greta2.cpp -o greta2
$ ./greta2
Hello World!

nbatfai@robopsy:~$]]>
                        </screen>
                        <para>
                            and that was followed by a good solution:
                        </para>
                        <programlisting language="C++">
<![CDATA[#include <iostream>

int main()
{
