                    <para>
                        Because it could happen that in the third battle the <literal>Nandi</literal>'s HP is 60 again when it went down to zero before! Let's see a great solution finally, just put one 'and' sign after the Soldier class:
	       </para>
                     
                    <programlisting language="C++">
